	<region id="editorData">
		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1) Go to Act 3 -&gt; Bhaal Temple.&#xD;&#xA;2) oe BTEnableAbduction&#xD;&#xA;3) Open Camp Debug book and add Laezel into camp.&#xD;&#xA;4) Go to camp or LongRest.&#xD;&#xA;5) Orin as Laezel with Yenna will appear in a Campfire Moment camp night.&#xD;&#xA;6) In the dialog with Orin-Laezel, do NOT provoke Orin to kill Yenna.&#xD;&#xA;7) Yenna survives after Orin leaves.&#xD;&#xA;8) Talk to Yenna." />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="21" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Orin abductions Laezel. In the CFM, Orin-Laezel takes Yenna as hostage. Players could encourage Orin-Laezel to murder Yenna. But this dialog is when players spared her and talked to her after the encounter." />
